Mary-Margaret Humes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary-Margaret_Humes 0 Mary-Margaret Humes (born April 4, 1954) is an American actress best known in recent years for playing Gail Leery, the title character's mother on the WB television drama Dawson's Creek from 1998 to 2003.
